        "pid": "152798874",
        "id": "note27",
        "text": "<p data-aid=\"152800089\" id=\"note27_p1\">RussellÂ M. Nelson, \u201c<a class=\"cross-ref\" href=\"/study/general-conference/2017/10/the-book-of-mormon-what-would-your-life-be-like-without-it?lang=eng&amp;para=39#p39\">The Book of Mormon: What Would Your Life Be Like without It?<\/a>,\u201d <cite>Ensign<\/cite> or <cite>Liahona<\/cite>, Nov. 2017, 62\u201363.<\/p>",
        "referenceUris": [{
          "href": "/study/general-conference/2017/10/the-book-of-mormon-what-would-your-life-be-like-without-it?lang=eng&amp;para=39#p39",
